  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Merling_King_and_the_Moon-Pale_Maiden_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/38/The_Merling_King_and_the_Moon-Pale_Maiden_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/350px-The_Merling_King_and_the_Moon-Pale_Maiden_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"266\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/38/The_Merling_King_and_the_Moon-Pale_Maiden_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/525px-The_Merling_King_and_the_Moon-Pale_Maiden_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/38/The_Merling_King_and_the_Moon-Pale_Maiden_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/700px-The_Merling_King_and_the_Moon-Pale_Maiden_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Merling_King_and_the_Moon-Pale_Maiden_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Moon-Pale Maiden and the <a href=\"/index.php/Merling_King\" title=\"Merling King\">Merling King</a>, by Jota Saraiva</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Moon-Pale Maiden</b> is a goddess. There is a statue of it in the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Black_and_White\" title=\"House of Black and White\">House of Black and White</a>. The statue is most commonly visited by sailors.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moon-Pale_Maiden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\